{ The last lecture of the camp is basically a theoretical overview of the variation } 1. e4 c6 2. d4 d5 3. Nc3 dxe4 4. Nxe4 Nf6 5. Nxf6+ exf6 { This lecture consists of theoretical analysis which is designed to complete your repertoire for Black. The idea here is not to cover every single move that White has at his disposal. At the same time, all the critical lines are covered in great detail. Additionally, you will find further explanations regarding the typical ideas and structures. } *
